library(dplyr)

library(ggplot2)
plot_data <- 
  get_plot_data() %>%
  filter_(~grepl("dplyr_df", name))
plot_data %>%
  tidyr::nest(-name) %>%
  purrr::by_row(
    function(plot_data_slice) {
      ggplot(plot_data_slice$data[[1]] %>% filter(!is.na(type)), aes(x = commit_id, y = median_time / 1e9)) +
        geom_line(data = plot_data_slice$data[[1]]) +
        geom_point(color = "red") +
        ggrepel::geom_label_repel(aes(label = substr(sha, 1, 7)), color = "red", alpha = 0.5) +
        scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, NA)) +
        ggtitle(plot_data_slice$name)
    }) %>%
  .$.out
